Five per-loop controller models (GRUController for PC, LC, FC, TC; CCSequenceModel for CC) predict control variable (CV) sequences independently from their observed history. The predicted CVs feed into the GRU Plant alongside the observed sensor window $x_{cv}$ and scenario embedding $\mathbf{e}_s$. The decoder autoregressively generates all five PV predictions, with no runtime feedback from  PVs to controllers.

